{
 "name": "RPlog_Very_Interesting...",
 "title": "Very Interesting...: Mayhem in Fountain Square",
 "summary": "In Plaxton's Fountain Square on Caspar, the spice-addled mercenary Axel Vichten joins the exiled former Imperials Antoine Dareus and Lynae Caiton, offering to bankroll their medical care and recruit their talents while grumbling that the Empire captured Danik Kreldin--whom he was promised the chance to hunt. Lynae, kept on borrowed time by a sabotaged pacemaker, repeatedly fights to stay calm amid the tense reunion, the arrival of Dareus's furious pregnant fiancee Kiare, and the sudden appearance of Darth Malign on a wheezing swoop. When the spiced-up Axel hurls his grievances and a knee at the Sith, Malign telekinetically launches him across the square into the fountain; a humiliated, concussed Axel draws a hand-cannon and fires wildly until a chunk of marble knocks him out cold. As constables, a Marine, the laughing Chadra-fan Wibble, and the watching Warlord Korolov turn the scene to chaos, Lynae collapses and recovers, the medics cart Axel off to a high-security hospital wing, and the battered group resolves never to leave the beach again.",
